2. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes an algorithm to solve the problem in O(n log n) time, which is a key area of research in data structures and algorithms. 
3. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) - The paper involves finding the minimum area triangle, which is a problem in discrete mathematics. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with finding triangles in the plane, which is a key area of research in computer graphics. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a solution to a geometric problem, which can be applied in control systems and robotics.
